Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了结束圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理由早已成次要的玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我早在那时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一直不知道就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变得希望这样过下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得不希望失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王特意前来相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一味默默站着不觉无礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 Saber赢不了这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:01:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 我我至少能防住第一击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请趁那机会...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 该逃的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好碰运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再投影一次Saber的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以

Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,360)\fad(800,0)}{\bord0\fs55\fnSimHei}天地初开洪荒世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这时杀了Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让Saber活下去还得花掉工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是再啰嗦的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这模样 似乎还不打算投靠我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力还是没变啊 这才是狮子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是本王看中的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在你那剑的分上 让你见识下我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate Of Babylon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,30)}<Gate Of Babylon>: 王之财宝  连接巴比伦的宝库的空间之门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是问我的真正身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个英灵怎么可能拥有那么多宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的轻率了Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最遥远的古代 当世界尚归于一元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下的财宝都是属唯一的王的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当世界尚归于一元时...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的真名乃人类史上最古老的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gilgamesh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对此身英灵绝无取胜之道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 不试试又怎知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王也不得不拿出相应之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除这英雄王以外无人可使役之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ex
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enuma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}天地初开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,calibur
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}洪荒世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:34.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<Enuma Elish>: 埃努玛.埃立什  根据苏美人的神话埃努玛.埃立什神创造了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人类最强的圣剑也就此等程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连抵挡下都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了  我应该手下留情一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说对手也是纤弱女子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎...你在 那里吗..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我马上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉... 请务必一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么总是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影吗 无聊的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所持的"选定王的石中剑"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应是北欧的"赋予支配的树中剑"所流传之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"赋予支配的树中剑"：即北欧英雄齐格弗里德\N所持有的魔剑Caladbolg
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这把更是其原型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劣化的复制怎可能与原型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匹敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的 是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说 肯成为我的所属咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 已经是没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么你就是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样害你死掉  我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你给我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就不要再独立一个人撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 比起我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这种东西 自己的性命应该...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有比Saber更想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能代替你的东西 在我心中根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以绝不把你交给那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁用得着你来允许
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚吧 英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让Saber活下去要花点工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭掉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想能赢的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该想像的 最强的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂死挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来士郎 就是我的鞘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的国家就要灭亡了 亚瑟王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么开始不把王位让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不适合做王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦 Saber的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 被他砍中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一直睡到刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的伤已经差不多全治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 saber呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 又...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 相信还会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉他像是故意放过我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要想得到圣杯就一定要打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了重新选定王...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起来的话 最好还是吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做点吃的去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已看士郎和凛做很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那能教教我怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样 转动萝卜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要重新选王了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看到了你的梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经很好的信守誓言了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到圣杯后 希望你能留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己而微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有什么好谈的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要为难我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢被这样被抱着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你可以把我推开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎太卑鄙了 知道了我的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几次进入我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道我的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道我所犯下的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢上你 有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让Saber就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然并不合适 但我毕竟被选定为国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然职责未能完成 像这种...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种自由 没有资格享有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力已恢复完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以随时战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言峰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想问他吉尔伽美什的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回去 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要来 这里没人的 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下 不可以下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言峰不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有 什么人也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下圣殿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事... 不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你来 卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算是教会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自进入到深处也是有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:09.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,360)\fad(800,0)}{\bord0\fs62\fnSimHei}愿望的尽头


Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:32.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きらめく涙は星に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:32.91,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶瑩的淚水化做了星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:37.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に乗り空を飾る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:37.33,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著風裝飾著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月明かり雲に途切れでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.80,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光即使被雲所遮蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:48.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:48.46,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也依就能照耀著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まっすぐなレルが嫌で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.99,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡筆直的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:04.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇雲駆け出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:04.59,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要自己闖出天地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諦めを決意に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.72,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化自棄為決心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨り減ったかっかと誇る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.37,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以磨爛鞋底為誇耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:22.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道は続く西へ東へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:22.32,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路無邊無際 向西向東
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:26.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日が沈んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:26.07,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使太陽西落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:32.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きらめく涙は星に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:32.89,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶瑩的淚水化做了星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:37.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に乗り空を飾る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:37.25,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘風而起點綴天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月明かり雲に途切れでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.74,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光即使被雲所遮蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:48.48,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也依然能照耀我

Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:17.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深い深い森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:17.71,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃的森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:23.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仄か香る愛しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:23.98,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微微的香氣惹人憐愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:30.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日々の面影探してみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:30.63,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找尋那熟悉的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:36.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不意に あなたが笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:36.46,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經意間看到你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:42.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸れてみたくて　手を伸ばしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:42.93,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想觸摸你 卻看不到你 伸出手來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:49.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儚く宙を舞ったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:49.41,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是在宇宙中浮雲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴方に會いたくて　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.30,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見你 一直想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:59.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會いたくて ずっと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:59.20,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見你 一直想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:03.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠れぬ夜を渡り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:03.61,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過長眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:11.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴方が殘した光と影の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:11.73,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光與影之間也留下了你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:19.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包まれて泣いている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:19.57,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:31.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深い深い森の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:31.90,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃的森林中

